com.safenetinc.jcprov.constants

Class CKK

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.safenetinc.jcprov.constants.CK_KEY_TYPE
      • com.safenetinc.jcprov.constants.CKK

  • public class CKK
extends CK_KEY_TYPE
    Class defining Cryptoki CKK_ constants - Key Type constants.

    Further information concerning the various key types is provided in the PKCS#11 standard and the Programmers Manual.
